---
title: Minestrone-Inspired Tortellini Soup with Cheesy Croutons
description: Tonight's dinner is an Italian classic! Warming and filling minestrone soup gets an upgrade with cheese-filled tortellini. A sprinkle of shredded parm is the perfect finishing touch to this hearty weeknight meal.
